rightHandSide.value: Angry Locals

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "While exploring you scare away a herd of beasts. The hunters that have been tracking them for days is not happy about this. They attack you."

rightHandSide.value: While exploring you scare away a herd of beasts. The hunters that have been tracking them for days is not happy about this. They attack you.
Shrieking Beasts

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "With a chorus of piercing shrieks, beasts decend upon you. They attack you."

rightHandSide.value: With a chorus of piercing shrieks, beasts decend upon you. They attack you.
Winged Beasts

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "Flying creatures soar above you. They dive out of the sky and attack you."

rightHandSide.value: Flying creatures soar above you. They dive out of the sky and attack you.
Shadow Creatures

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "Shadows move and materialize. This combat is treated as if it is night. If it is already night, increase night penalty by 1."

rightHandSide.value: Shadows move and materialize. This combat is treated as if it is night. If it is already night, increase night penalty by 1.
Ancient Guardian

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "An ancient guardian awakens and attacks you. You cannot escape."

rightHandSide.value: An ancient guardian awakens and attacks you. You cannot escape.
Deathbot Activated

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "The whirring of machinery. Death to organics. A deathbot attacks you."

rightHandSide.value: The whirring of machinery. Death to organics. A deathbot attacks you.
Clumsy Misstep

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "You lose your footing and drop an item. "

rightHandSide.value: You lose your footing and drop an item.
Marooned Pirate

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "You trip over what you thought was a dead body. Rather it is a Marauder comfortably sleeping off some space rum. He is not happy about that and attacks you."

rightHandSide.value: You trip over what you thought was a dead body. Rather it is a Marauder comfortably sleeping off some space rum. He is not happy about that and attacks you.
Flesh Eating Insects

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "Ouch! You start to feel stings all over your body."

rightHandSide.value: Ouch! You start to feel stings all over your body.
Ghastly Apparition

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "A terrifying feeling chills your bones. You don't take the time to find out what it is."

rightHandSide.value: A terrifying feeling chills your bones. You don't take the time to find out what it is.

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "Before you realize the ground is not solid, you fall into what appears to be an animal trap."

rightHandSide.value: Before you realize the ground is not solid, you fall into what appears to be an animal trap.

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "The ground is sticky, you are unable to move."

rightHandSide.value: The ground is sticky, you are unable to move.

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "You hear a rumble, a boulder tumbles toward you."

rightHandSide.value: You hear a rumble, a boulder tumbles toward you.

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "The sun is blotted from the sky."

rightHandSide.value: The sun is blotted from the sky.

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "You hear voices in your head beckoning you to follow them."

rightHandSide.value: You hear voices in your head beckoning you to follow them.

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "You are suddenly struck with inexplicable terror."

rightHandSide.value: You are suddenly struck with inexplicable terror.
Meteorite Strike

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "A streak of fire smashes into the ground at your feet."

rightHandSide.value: A streak of fire smashes into the ground at your feet.
Cryo Mine

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "As you take a step you hear a click and a beep. Before you can react you hear an explosion."

rightHandSide.value: As you take a step you hear a click and a beep. Before you can react you hear an explosion.

typeDescriptions.typeString: literal_string "The vegetation around you seems to come alive. It grasps you tightly."

typeDescriptions.typeString: function (string memory[] memory,string memory[] memory,uint16[] memory)

getRoleAdmin(bytes32).details: Returns the admin role that controls `role`. See {grantRole} and {revokeRole}. To change a role's admin, use {_setRoleAdmin}.

getRoleMember(bytes32,uint256).details: Returns one of the accounts that have `role`. `index` must be a value between 0 and {getRoleMemberCount}, non-inclusive. Role bearers are not sorted in any particular way, and their ordering may change at any point. WARNING: When using {getRoleMember} and {getRoleMemberCount}, make sure you perform all queries on the same block. See the following https://forum.openzeppelin.com/t/iterating-over-elements-on-enumerableset-in-openzeppelin-contracts/2296[forum post] for more information.

getRoleMemberCount(bytes32).details: Returns the number of accounts that have `role`. Can be used together with {getRoleMember} to enumerate all bearers of a role.

grantRole(bytes32,address).details: Grants `role` to `account`. If `account` had not been already granted `role`, emits a {RoleGranted} event. Requirements: - the caller must have ``role``'s admin role.

renounceRole(bytes32,address).details: Revokes `role` from the calling account. Roles are often managed via {grantRole} and {revokeRole}: this function's purpose is to provide a mechanism for accounts to lose their privileges if they are compromised (such as when a trusted device is misplaced). If the calling account had been revoked `role`, emits a {RoleRevoked} event. Requirements: - the caller must be `account`.

revokeRole(bytes32,address).details: Revokes `role` from `account`. If `account` had been granted `role`, emits a {RoleRevoked} event. Requirements: - the caller must have ``role``'s admin role.
